title: US and German transportation heads to meet over Volkswagen woes
text:
US and German transportation heads to meet over Volkswagen woes 
Cnet Saturday 24th October, 2015 
The fallout from Volkswagen's diesel emissions scandal isn't over yet. Germany's minister of transportation will meet with US federal officials next week amid plummeting diesel resale values, expanding vehicle recalls and a missing investigation file. Governments and the general public continue to scrutinize Volkswagen after the German automaker last month...
